### EduPortal API - Visa Processes Controller
### Visa process management endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000
### Requires Authentication

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/visa-processes
@contentType = application/json
@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}

### ===========================================
### GET ALL VISA PROCESSES - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET ACTIVE VISA PROCESSES - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/active
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET PENDING VISA PROCESSES - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET EXPIRING VISAS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### Default: 90 days
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/expiring?days=90
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET VISA PROCESS BY ID - (Admin, Coach, Danışman, Ogrenci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET VISA PROCESSES BY PROGRAM - (Admin, Coach, Danışman, Ogrenci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/program/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET VISA TIMELINE - (Admin, Coach, Danışman, Ogrenci)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/1/timeline
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### GET VISA STATISTICS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/statistics
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ===========================================
### CREATE VISA PROCESS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "studyAbroadProgramId": 1,
  "visaType": "F1",
  "applicationDate": "2024-06-01",
  "appointmentDate": "2024-07-15",
  "status": "DocumentPreparation",
  "notes": "Vize başvurusu başlatıldı"
}

### ===========================================
### UPDATE VISA PROCESS - (Admin, Coach, Danışman)
### ===========================================
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "Approved",
  "approvalDate": "2024-07-20",
  "visaNumber": "VN123456789",
  "expiryDate": "2029-07-20",
  "notes": "Vize onaylandı"
}

### ===========================================
### DELETE VISA PROCESS - (Admin only)
### ===========================================
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

